event.name: Ropsten Testnet Merge Protocol Supporter
event.description:
The Ropsten Testnet successfully merged the Execution and Consensus clients on June 8, 2022. This initial public testnet merge is an important technical milestone for the Ethereum network that paves the way for other testnets and the Mainnet merge. Holders of this POAP showed their support of the Ethereum protocol by sending 1 dollar of value to Protocol Guild within the specified time ranges on the day of the testnet merge. The cumulative amount raised is over $11,000, which will be disbursed directly to the Ethereum Core Developers. Thank you for celebrating this historic event with the rest of the community.
- https://ethereum.org
- https://guildprotocol.io
- https://ethstaker.cc
Design by Samagraphico#7571 from Poapathon.com

event.name: blr dev cartel genesis
event.description:
Thanks for attending our IRL meetup! This commemorates the start of our dev cartel.

I noticed a lack of dev cartels in India, and that prompted me to create one, as simple as that!

This is a house for hardcore dev stuff, to share knowledge, and help others with technical and architectural problems. There's also a lot of geek talk that kinda gets lost in translation, so this is a safe space to talk about the latest exploit or rug pull 😆

We'll also have a lot of fun and chill! So if you know hardcore devs(devs only!), send them an invite to this group, and let's grow it organically!

event.name: Preme Profits Founding Member
event.description: This is our (literal) token of thanks to our members as of May 11 2021. In the last almost three years since August 17 2018, we have together built an amazing community around financial independence and becoming your own boss. Before our next wave of members, we want to show thanks to the people that got us here: we will be running weekly raffles in perpetuity ONLY for Founding Member badge holders still in Preme Profits while the raffles are being held. You'll have to manually enter each week's raffle from a link we'll send in #announcements and DM us on Discord with proof of your Ethereum address to claim your prize. In true PremeProfits fashion, these are also resellable if you port them to the Ethereum main chain and sell on a marketplace such as OpenSea. (however, in order to take part in the raffles if you bought the badge from the secondary market, you must also be a current PremeProfits member at the time of raffle entry, as the only way to redeem is via the PremeProfits discord.) Special thanks to the designer of our first NFT, Andre Camero (@holygrxil)
